{"tid":1308211,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"連儂牆係大家要爭取既野咩？","createTime":"2019-07-11T23:56:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T00:09:38.000Z","uid":30408,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6ee3bf3da5d7f415b73c2a565998c57a4e500f9b","tid":1308211,"uid":30408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T23:56:02.000Z","msg":"唔該大家唔好為幅牆做到上曬腦咁<br />\n深藍地方都話又去搞 廢老因爲啲紙仔同你去溝通？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔會</span></span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">因為嘈得嗰啲都係無曬理性</span></span><br />\n不指責無問題 但搞深藍地區既發起人可唔可以講下<br />\n學生同女仔唔洗參與 再唔係搵多啲大隻仔幫手呢<br />\n唔好由班手足去比廢老打或者非禮<br />\n<br />\n前幾日巴打比人打我睇到好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好彩無事 <br />\n但都只係有片既情況班狗先無得唔拉 <br />\n學生或女仔北角萬一比廢老拉走咗<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>無人影到佢對你地做咩都無仇報<br />\n至少無片班狗都唔會落力捉</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">唔好咁傻以為可以加輿論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n我真係寧願無手足再受傷害<br />\n心靈創傷一世架 牆只係心意<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">要守既唔係牆 係烈士同全港義士既心願</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8dw0pUi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8dw0pUi.png&h=07764fda&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ef1d29b3788110a3017a771ebe11aa234d83434c","tid":1308211,"uid":30408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T23:56:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6de397322212bee47eab59a3762a4e59c3ec6a0e","tid":1308211,"uid":30408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T23:58:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>請立即停手，我而家嚴重警告你，唔好再襲擊<br />\n我而家係制止你再打人，請立即停手<br />\n我而家係公民拘捕你，因為你對我朋友施以實質傷害的襲擊</strong></span>"},{"pid":"d1fc1c3001e06bebb58751e6a312e6726258aa3f","tid":1308211,"uid":30408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T23:59:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"15069a149aa53de445e510f4eaa14a38a27d07c6","tid":1308211,"uid":30408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T23:59:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"03a639abd4b10410f2d8c80c74792e5fa0340905","tid":1308211,"uid":30408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T23:59:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"af75565c5caca0818a5a366f22a34c703c60d9e7","tid":1308211,"uid":30408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T00:00:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"492b23cad19775fea285f75fb71d476e945c6d1f","tid":1308211,"uid":30408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T00:01:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"627f1585f2b3f93ec1ec57af17408262a9f68274","tid":1308211,"uid":30408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T00:01:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d2658b67a3e9602fe1f76a089fdadaa4d9e99b94","tid":1308211,"uid":30408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T00:02:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"68c094f0dad52d76bf01b6e77adcf82487854756","tid":1308211,"uid":30408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T00:03:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"12fa43a250c56bcc6b339534fb34600574cba68f","tid":1308211,"uid":30408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T00:03:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"36a228ea8c1014ecb80f6d7f02c6bb4e60993a7e","tid":1308211,"uid":30408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T00:03:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"540f6f1e596738ad9ec156d24e6ca005da438de0","tid":1308211,"uid":30408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T00:03:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3bee58760339d2780b23a21c3cc8911bc5d4f3ab","tid":1308211,"uid":30408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T00:03:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b37144159590605ffd6542bbf0c